Facebook post by Noorie Noor Ananta, 1 January 2019. Text on image: 'Looking for truth? Observe people's habitual behavior patterns/cycles. The truth is in their patterns and cycles. Not so much their words.' This is teaching discernment through observation of cycles — directly connecting to the Yug Parivartan understanding that cosmic ages follow cycles. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Wisdom Teaching — truth is found in patterns and cycles, not words.
